  "text": "beforeUnmount triggered before mounted\n\n### Version\r\n3.2.27\r\n\r\n### Reproduction link\r\n[sfc.vuejs.org/](https://sfc.vuejs.org/#)\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n### Steps to reproduce\r\nplease review the reproduction code, when organizing the code like this，will happen beforeUnmount is executed before mounted.\r\n\r\nif the component  `Comp` not use `v-if=\"flag\"，work find. Because，`render` function  whill executed `flushPostFlushCbs()` after patch.\r\n\r\n### What is expected?\r\nbeforeUnmount triggered before mounted\r\n\r\n### What is actually happening?\r\nbeforeUnmount triggered after mounted\r\n\r\n<!-- generated by vue-issues. DO NOT REMOVE -->",
